
Installation instructions
=========================
This project uses Puppet for installing all dependencies.
Puppet installation instructions are available here:

http://docs.puppetlabs.com/guides/installation.html

Make sure to install the necessary puppet extensions:

> sudo puppet module install puppetlabs/java

Installation of development machine
-----------------------------------
> sudo puppet apply install/dev.pp

Run development server
----------------------
> ./manage.py runserver

Compile install packages to ./dist on developer machine
-------------------------------------------------------
> ./setup.py build sdist

Installation of production web server
-------------------------------------
> sudo puppet apply install/prod_web.pp

Installation of production backend server
-----------------------------------------
> sudo puppet apply install/prod_backend.pp

Install new release on production machine
------------------------------------------
> tar xvfz FuzzEdx.xx.tgz .
> ./manage.py syncdb
> ./manage.py migrate

